lyrics: Lyrics: Display lyrics for current song from Genius.com
pause: Pause: Stop playback of current song
play: Play+(Search Terms): Searches Spotify for search terms, and adds first result to queue
queue: Queue: Displays queue of upcoming songs
remove: Remove+#: Removes the #th position. If no # is given, removes most recently queued song
resume: Resume: Resumes playback of current song
voteskip: Voteskip: Initiates a vote to skip
